issue.title: contact us banner is blocking the feedback submit button
issue.body:
Expected:
Be able to click the submit button on the feedback form, with the banner below it

Reality:
banner is blocking the feedback button.

Possible solutions:
1. add padding to the form so that page can scroll down further and button can be seen
2. make banner smaller (recommended)

![screenshot 2013-08-09 at 12 13 45](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/191955/940248/d960cd7c-0127-11e3-85f8-3e23586fa3f7.png)
